OL,3,CSearch underway for two children
OL,4,Cmissing off Jersey's east coast
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Fabout the whereabouts of two 10-year-
OL,8,Fold boys who were last seen off the
OL,9,Feast coast of Jersey.
OL,11,FThe children, who are described as
OL,12,Fhaving dark hair and being five feet
OL,13,Ftall, were seen in the sea on an
OL,14,Finflatable paddleboard at Archirondel.
OL,16,FThe inflatable washed up on the beach
OL,17,F15 minutes later with the boys nowhere
OL,18,Fto be seen.
